name: New World by VES3L Ad
description:
New World will be my second collection on fxhash. You received this airdrop because you own a work from my prior collection Intertwined.

Collecting:
Minting starts Mon. March 14, 12:00pm EST.

There will be 199 editions priced with a Dutch Auction starting at 16xtz, decreasing every 10 minutes by 4xtz until the minimum of 8xtz.

The collection will be listed here once published: https://www.fxhash.xyz/u/VES3L

Charity:
5% of primary sales will be donated to Ukrainian humanitarian aid funds through the contract set up by ciphrd and Veqtor.

Presale:
To reward existing collectors of my work, those who own 4 or more Intertwined pieces are entitled to 2 presale reservations at 8xtz. The presale supply is 20 editions and the allocation will be distributed on a first-come-first-serve basis.

The snapshot of Intertwined holders will be taken on March 9 at 11:59pm EST. DM me after the snapshot if you’re interested in reserving and qualify based on this criteria.
